---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageWrapper from "../components/layouts/PageWrapper.astro";
import "../styles/about.css";
---

<Layout title="Now - KTTLSAA">
  <PageWrapper>
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h1 class="about-title">Now: May 2nd 2025</h1>
        
        <div class="about-section">
          <p>
            This is an incomplete and continuously changing list of the subjects & projects I currently find interesting and want to explore more. It isn't a list of everything I'm doing but rather a snapshot of where my energy and curiosity are primarily directed <em>right now</em>. Here is a site on <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Now Pages</a>.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            My current deep dive is into <strong>human knowledge and the remarkable organ that creates and holds it â€“ the human brain.</strong> I'm driven by a desire to find ways to celebrate these fundamental aspects of who we are.
            Working on concepts that make the journey of learning visible and exciting.
          </p>
          
          <div class="about-quote">
            <p>
              If you share this fascination with the human mind and the celebration of knowledge, I'd genuinely appreciate you <a href="/about">getting in touch</a>. I'm always open to connecting with kindred spirits and discussing potential collaborative explorations.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="last-updated">
            Last updated: May 2nd 2025
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </PageWrapper>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Inherit styles from about.css and add specific styles for now page */
  .about-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-s, 1rem);
    font-family: "Averia Serif Libre", serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f2937;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl, 3rem);
  }
  
  .about-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m, 1.5rem);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  
  .about-section a {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .about-section a:hover {
    color: #ff8c00;
    border-bottom-color: #ff8c00;
  }
  
  .about-quote {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    padding: var(--space-m, 1.5rem);
    border-left: 3px solid #ff8c00;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    margin: var(--space-l, 2rem) 0;
  }
  
  .about-quote p {
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: right;
    margin-top: 3rem !important;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: var(--space-l, 2rem) var(--space-s, 1rem);
    }
    
    .about-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .about-quote {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: var(--space-s, 1rem);
    }
  }
</style>


